# DSMprops/conus100m

<!-- badges: start -->

<!-- badges: end -->

This folder houses various folders housing scripts used to produce property prediction maps and for other general steps in producing SOLUS 100m maps. Each property has a folder in addition to a post processing and analysis folder.
